Implementation of trilinear interpolation: 1. c_00 = V[x_0,y_0,z_0] * (1 - x_d) + V[x_1,y_0,z_0] * x_d 2. c_10 = V[x_0,y_1,z_0] * (1 - x_d) + V[x_1,y_1,z_0] * x_d 3. c_01 = V[x_0,y_0,z_1] * (1 - x_d) + V[x_1,y_0,z_1] * x_d 4. c_11 = V[x_0,y_1,z_1] * (1 - x_d) + V[x_1,y_1,z_1] * x_d 5. c_0 = c_00 * (1 - y_d) + c_10 * y_d 6. c_1 = c_01 * (1 - y_d) + c_11 * y_d 7. c = c_0 * (1 - z_d) + c_1 * z_d
